---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import HeaderEn from '../../components/HeaderEn.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_LAST_UPDATED_EN } from '../../consts';
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <BaseHead
    title="About Miao He — Dual-Licensed Family Lawyer Toronto | Ontario & China | H. LAW FIRM"
    description="Miao He (何淼) is dual-licensed in Ontario and China, with 15+ years of GTA family law experience. Expert Witness in Chinese family law, Notary Public, Osgoode Hall LL.M. 647-930-6688."
  />
  <meta name="keywords" content="Miao He lawyer,Mia He lawyer,Chinese family lawyer Toronto,dual licensed China Canada lawyer,Expert Witness Chinese marriage law,Notary Public Markham,Osgoode family lawyer,Ontario China bar licensed" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="About Miao He — Dual-Licensed Family Lawyer Toronto" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="profile" />
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="zh" href="https://www.miaohelaw.ca/about/" />
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://www.miaohelaw.ca/en/about/" />
  <script type="application/ld+json">{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Person",
    "name": "Miao He",
    "alternateName": ["何淼", "Mia He"],
    "jobTitle": "Family Law Lawyer",
    "url": "https://www.miaohelaw.ca/en/about/",
    "telephone": "+1-647-930-6688",
    "email": "miao@miaohelaw.ca",
    "image": "https://www.miaohelaw.ca/miao-he-about-hero.jpg",
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "streetAddress": "208-7050 Woodbine Ave",
      "addressLocality": "Markham",
      "addressRegion": "Ontario",
      "addressCountry": "CA"
    },
    "alumniOf": {"@type": "CollegeOrUniversity", "name": "Osgoode Hall Law School, York University"},
    "memberOf": {"@type": "Organization", "name": "Law Society of Ontario", "identifier": "83315K"},
    "worksFor": {"@type": "LegalService", "name": "H. LAW FIRM", "url": "https://www.miaohelaw.ca/en/"}
  }</script>
  <script type="application/ld+json">{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      {"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"name":"Home","item":"https://www.miaohelaw.ca/en/"},
      {"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"name":"About","item":"https://www.miaohelaw.ca/en/about/"}
    ]
  }</script>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    /*
      Match site-wide English typography (global.css): editorial serif body + display headings.
      Keep Atkinson only on buttons (UI affordances), not long-form copy.
    */
    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      letter-spacing: 0.002em;
    }
    a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { color: var(--accent-dark); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
    .page { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    .page--who { padding-top: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem); }
    .page h1 {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", var(--font-en-display) !important;
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 4.8vw, 3.25rem);
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      line-height: 1.08;
      color: var(--text-heading);
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }
    .who-hero h1 {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", var(--font-en-display) !important;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.2vw, 2.85rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      line-height: 1.12;
      color: var(--text-heading);
      margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
    }
    .content-card { background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #E8E0D5; border-radius: 8px; padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .content-card h2 {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", var(--font-en-display) !important;
      color: #8B6914;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .content-card p { color: #5A4A3A; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .content-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
    .content-card ul li { color: #5A4A3A; font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 0.3rem 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; position: relative; }
    .content-card ul li::before { content: "·"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #8B6914; }
    .cred-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .cred-item { border: 1px solid #E8E0D5; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .cred-item .icon { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .cred-item .title {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", var(--font-en-display) !important;
      color: var(--text-heading);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }
    .cred-item .desc { color: #7A6A5A; font-size: 0.78rem; margin-top: 0.2rem; }
    .case-block { background: #F5EFE0; border-left: 3px solid #D4A853; padding: 1rem 1.2rem; border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .case-block h3 { color: var(--text-heading); font-size: 0.92rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .case-block p { color: #7A6A5A; font-size: 0.82rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .case-block a { color: #8B6914; font-size: 0.8rem; }
    .contact-box { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; }
    .contact-box h2 { color: #8B6914; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #D4A853;
      color: var(--text-heading);
      padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-family: "Atkinson", ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, "SF Pro Text", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin: 0.5rem;
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      display: inline-block;
      border: 1px solid #D4A853;
      color: #8B6914;
      padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-family: "Atkinson", ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, "SF Pro Text", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0.5rem;
    }
    /* ── WHO WE ARE: full-bleed office bg + scrim + cutout (left) + copy (right) ── */
    .who-hero--studio{
      position: relative;
      isolation: isolate;
      min-height: clamp(460px, 62vh, 680px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end;
    }
    .who-hero-bg{
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .who-hero-bg-image{
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: url("/about-hero-office.jpg");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: 58% center;
      transform: scale(1.03);
    }
    .who-hero-bg-overlay{
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(
        100deg,
        rgba(247, 242, 239, 0.18) 0%,
        rgba(247, 242, 239, 0.52) 24%,
        rgba(247, 242, 239, 0.86) 46%,
        rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.94) 100%
      );
    }
    .who-hero-shell{
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      width: 100%;
      padding: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.75rem) 0 clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.75rem);
    }
    .who-hero-inner{
      max-width: 1120px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 0.75rem;
    }
    .who-hero-grid{
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(200px, 4fr) minmax(0, 8fr);
      gap: clamp(0.9rem, 2.2vw, 1.75rem);
      align-items: stretch;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .who-portrait{
      margin: 0;
      align-self: stretch;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      line-height: 0;
      min-height: 0;
    }
    .who-portrait img{
      width: auto;
      max-width: min(380px, 100%);
      max-height: 85%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto 0 -10px;
      object-fit: contain;
      object-position: center center;
      transform: translateY(10px);
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.42);
      box-shadow:
        0 14px 34px rgba(122, 90, 26, 0.1),
        0 6px 16px rgba(184, 150, 120, 0.18);
    }
    .who-copy{ min-width: 0; padding-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .who-rule{
      width: 3.5rem;
      height: 3px;
      border-radius: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #7a5a1a, rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.85));
      margin: 0.25rem 0 1.05rem;
    }
    .who-kicker{
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.55rem 0.65rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      font-family: var(--font-en-body) !important;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(122, 90, 26, 0.65);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .who-kicker-line{
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      width: 2.35rem;
      height: 2px;
      border-radius: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #7a5a1a, rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.82));
    }
    .who-kicker-inner{
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .who-kicker-ico{
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: rgba(212,168,83,0.18);
      color: #7A5A1A;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .who-lead{
      margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: rgba(44,24,16,0.86);
      font-family: var(--font-en-body) !important;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }
    .who-sub{
      margin: 0 0 1.35rem;
      padding-top: 1.05rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.28);
      font-size: 0.94rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: rgba(90,74,58,0.82);
      font-family: var(--font-en-body) !important;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }
    .who-checklist{
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0 0 1.55rem;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      max-width: 34rem;
    }
    .who-checklist li{
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.45rem;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: rgba(44,24,16,0.88);
      font-family: var(--font-en-body) !important;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      line-height: 1.45;
      padding: 0.45rem 1rem 0.45rem 0.75rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 252, 248, 0.98) 0%, rgba(247, 242, 239, 0.88) 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.4);
      box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75) inset;
    }
    .who-checklist li::before{
      content: "✓";
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      width: auto;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 0;
      display: block;
      margin-top: 0;
      background: transparent;
      color: rgba(122, 90, 26, 0.78);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .who-actions{
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.25rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .who-btn{
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 0.9rem 1.6rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(184,150,120,0.88);
      color: #fff;
      font-family: "Atkinson", ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, "SF Pro Text", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      text-decoration: none;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 34px rgba(44,24,16,0.14);
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, filter 0.15s ease;
    }
    .who-btn:hover{ transform: translateY(-1px); filter: brightness(1.02); }
    .who-last-updated{
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: rgba(90,74,58,0.72);
      font-family: var(--font-en-body) !important;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .cred-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .page { padding: 2rem 1rem; } }
    @media (max-width: 920px){
      .who-hero-grid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; text-align: center; }
      .who-portrait{ justify-content: center; align-self: center; width: 100%; max-width: min(320px, 88vw); }
      .who-portrait img{ margin: 0 auto; max-width: min(280px, 74vw); max-height: none; }
      .who-checklist{ align-items: center; max-width: none; width: 100%; }
      .who-checklist li{ max-width: min(26rem, 100%); }
      .who-actions{ justify-content: center; }
      .who-hero h1, .page h1{ text-align: center; }
      .who-kicker{ justify-content: center; width: 100%; }
      .who-rule{ margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
      .who-hero-bg-overlay{
        background: linear-gradient(
          165deg,
          rgba(247, 242, 239, 0.35) 0%,
          rgba(247, 242, 239, 0.82) 42%,
          rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.94) 100%
        );
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <HeaderEn />
  <section class="who-hero who-hero--studio" aria-labelledby="who-title">
    <div class="who-hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="who-hero-bg-image"></div>
      <div class="who-hero-bg-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="who-hero-shell">
      <div class="who-hero-inner">
        <div class="who-hero-grid">
          <figure class="who-portrait">
            <img
              src="/miao-he-about-hero.jpg"
              alt="Miao He — Ontario family law lawyer"
              width="682"
              height="1024"
              fetchpriority="high"
              decoding="async"
            />
          </figure>
          <div class="who-copy">
            <div class="who-kicker">
              <span class="who-kicker-line" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="who-kicker-inner">
                <span class="who-kicker-ico" aria-hidden="true">⚖️</span>
                <span>WHO WE ARE</span>
              </span>
            </div>
            <h1 id="who-title">Strategic Advocacy.<br />Cross-Border Expertise.</h1>
            <div class="who-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <p class="who-lead">
              Miao He (何淼) is a dual-licensed family lawyer in Ontario and China, with 15+ years of experience serving Chinese-Canadian families across the GTA.
            </p>
            <p class="who-sub">
              Litigator mindset, settlement strategy. High-conflict divorce, child custody, and complex cross-border assets — handled in Mandarin and English.
            </p>

            <ul class="who-checklist" aria-label="Key strengths">
              <li>Dual-licensed in Ontario &amp; China</li>
              <li>Courtroom-heavy practice — 20+ hours/month</li>
              <li>Mediation-trained — tactful, firm when needed</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="who-actions">
              <a href="tel:6479306688" class="who-btn">Book a consultation · 647-930-6688</a>
              <div class="who-last-updated">Page last updated: {SITE_LAST_UPDATED_EN}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="page page--who">
    <div class="content-card">
      <h2>ABOUT</h2>
      <p>I am Miao He (何淼), a dual-licensed family lawyer holding both an Ontario bar licence and a China bar licence. I have practiced family law in the Greater Toronto Area for over 15 years and serve as the principal lawyer at H. LAW FIRM, located in Markham.</p>
      <p>I appear in court over 20 hours per month and provide more than 200 legal consultations per year — making me one of the most active family lawyers serving the Chinese-Canadian community in the GTA.</p>
      <p>My philosophy is simple: <strong>negotiate when it makes sense, litigate when it is necessary.</strong> I hold a Mediation Certificate and can represent clients effectively in both court and non-court proceedings.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card">
      <h2>CREDENTIALS</h2>
      <div class="cred-grid">
        <div class="cred-item">
          <div class="icon">⚖️</div>
          <div class="title">Dual-Licensed Lawyer</div>
          <div class="desc">Law Society of Ontario #83315K · China Bar Association</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cred-item">
          <div class="icon">🎓</div>
          <div class="title">Osgoode Hall Law School</div>
          <div class="desc">Master of Laws (LL.M.) · York University</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cred-item">
          <div class="icon">🏛️</div>
          <div class="title">Expert Witness</div>
          <div class="desc">Court-appointed Expert Witness in Chinese Family Law & Marriage Law</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cred-item">
          <div class="icon">📋</div>
          <div class="title">Notary Public — Ontario</div>
          <div class="desc">Sworn statements, powers of attorney, documents for overseas use</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cred-item">
          <div class="icon">🤝</div>
          <div class="title">Mediation Certificate</div>
          <div class="desc">Certified mediator — negotiation and litigation strategy</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cred-item">
          <div class="icon">🏢</div>
          <div class="title">Professional Memberships</div>
          <div class="desc">TAS · TLA · YRLA · Justice Net</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card">
      <h2>PRACTICE AREAS</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Divorce — Contested & Uncontested</li>
        <li>Child Custody & Parenting Time</li>
        <li>Child & Spousal Support</li>
        <li>Equalization of Net Family Property</li>
        <li>Domestic Contracts (Marriage, Separation, Cohabitation Agreements)</li>
        <li>Cross-Border Asset Division — China & Canada</li>
        <li>High-Conflict Litigation & Enforcement Motions</li>
        <li>Emergency Motions</li>
        <li>Mediation & Arbitration</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card">
      <h2>THE DUAL-LICENCE ADVANTAGE</h2>
      <p>Holding both Ontario and China bar licences, I can directly investigate and handle assets held in China — real estate, company shares, and family trusts. This is a capability most Ontario lawyers simply do not have. In high-net-worth divorce cases involving cross-border assets, this makes a decisive difference.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card">
      <h2>REPRESENTATIVE CASES</h2>
      <div class="case-block">
        <h3>Yang v. Li, 2024 ONSC 4801</h3>
        <p>Represented the respondent against eight simultaneous claims including a CBV business valuation dispute. All eight claims defeated at motion. Costs awarded for lack of candour. Appeal unanimously dismissed by three Divisional Court judges.</p>
        <a href="https://www.canlii.org/en/on/onsc/doc/2024/2024onsc4801/2024onsc4801.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View on CanLII →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="case-block">
        <h3>Li v. Jiang, 2026 ONSC 561</h3>
        <p>Represented the applicant against a respondent who refused to cooperate with the sale of matrimonial property for 19 months. Successfully obtained an Unrestricted Access Order and $4,000 in costs.</p>
        <a href="https://www.canlii.org/en/on/onsc/doc/2026/2026onsc561/2026onsc561.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View on CanLII →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card">
      <h2>AREAS SERVED</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Toronto · Markham · Richmond Hill · Vaughan</li>
        <li>Mississauga · Scarborough · North York · Brampton</li>
        <li>Newmarket · Ajax · Pickering · Thornhill</li>
        <li>Ottawa · Hamilton · London · Windsor · All of Ontario</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card contact-box">
      <h2>Book a Consultation</h2>
      <p style="color:#5A4A3A; margin-bottom:1.5rem; font-size:0.9rem;">30 minutes · $220 + HST · Mandarin & English · Usually responds within 3 business days</p>
      <a href="tel:6479306688" class="btn-primary">📞 647-930-6688</a>
      <a href="mailto:miao@miaohelaw.ca" class="btn-secondary">Email Us</a>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer lang="en" />
</body>
</html>
